{"tid":1987833,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"露宿者：中招死 窮也會死","createTime":"2020-04-24T17:53:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-25T07:54:52.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e4066a980c4f151611b68a61af1743c6e25fbe98","tid":1987833,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T17:53:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200424/YDOQJJTBXWMQIQQHLQYDXUOS5U/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200424%2FYDOQJJTBXWMQIQQHLQYDXUOS5U%2F&d=6Js6kSUmrxq5WnxEZabkn1lsl4SrcEEyWLual4COuMU%3D&h=9584b305\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200424%2FYDOQJJTBXWMQIQQHLQYDXUOS5U%2F&h=47fc09f1\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200424/YDOQJJTBXWMQIQQHLQYDXUOS5U/</a><br />\n<br />\n露宿者：中招死 窮也會死<br />\n<br />\n留家抗疫從來不是露宿者有權利選擇，近月有基層因疫情失業而要露宿街頭。他們當中有人覺得染疫比貧窮可怕，有人視疫情和貧窮一樣致命，唯一共同目標只有求存。社區組織協會幹事吳衞東稱，本港逾千名露宿者中，約一半領綜援過活，另一半則有工作，以往絕少尋求協會幫助。惟1月開始，向該會申請緊急援助基金的個案明顯增加，「以往一個月會有5個人搵我哋，𠵱家一個月超過20人。」<br />\n<br />\n「自從冇嘢做之後，欠租3個月，最後業主鎖咗門，要瞓公園，都幾慘。」59歲的Peter在疫情中失業兼失家，被迫流落在通州街公園的長凳過夜，「天氣係毛毛雨，有少少風，坐到差唔多3點幾就睇小說，睇到攰就起身郁吓，到天光為止，都凍㗎。」他不想露宿，經吳衞東出面調解，業主才肯開鎖讓他有家可歸。<br />\n<br />\n任職酒樓點心師傅30多年的他，月入2萬多元，一直以3,000元月租深水埗劏房，但去年9月失去長工，轉靠兼職為生，自12月更連兼職也不保，經濟拮据，1月起連欠三個月租金，「同朋友借，借到𠵱家欠人哋3萬，借到朋友都發爛渣，冇得借啦！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200424/large/1587659778_2cb5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200424%2Flarge%2F1587659778_2cb5.jpg&h=e2e0f5b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n謝叔露宿六年，認為窮或染疫都是死路一條。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n害怕染病無錢醫<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：居病毒溫床 劏房戶：死咗冇人知<br />\n<br />\n重返劏房生活，Peter仍受疫情困擾，「講真擔心係擔心，呢啲（疫情）盡量避。𠵱家連外出都怕。」<br />\n<br />\nPeter坦言染疫比貧窮可怕，「瞓街仲有生存機會，中招呢，一來冇錢醫，二來有錢都未必醫得到。」<br />\n<br />\n另一露宿6年的謝叔，則視疫情和貧窮一樣致命，「窮係生活唔到，等於死啦；中咗招都係一樣，都係死。」現時他每月靠3,000多元綜援金過活，根本沒多餘錢購買抗疫物資，「擔心唔到，（口罩和搓手液）係教會送。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200424/large/1587659777_0041.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200424%2Flarge%2F1587659777_0041.jpg&h=4add9201&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n經過社區組織出面調解，業主才肯開鎖予欠租的Peter入房。"},{"pid":"c829c3699f01cbd8124af196a4c79aea7fec3c98","tid":1987833,"uid":11285,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T17:57:17.000Z","msg":"月入2萬幾三十年都可以唔儲錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"156d68c469ea7d210f795db871c6d52b604ae753","tid":1987833,"uid":28683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c829c3699f01cbd8124af196a4c79aea7fec3c98","tid":1987833,"uid":11285,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T17:57:17.000Z","msg":"月入2萬幾三十年都可以唔儲錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T18:08:35.000Z","msg":"賭撚哂啦"},{"pid":"f84f0dac9304320c41a21f241de941a1aafde4f0","tid":1987833,"uid":115655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"156d68c469ea7d210f795db871c6d52b604ae753","tid":1987833,"uid":28683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c829c3699f01cbd8124af196a4c79aea7fec3c98","tid":1987833,"uid":11285,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T17:57:17.000Z","msg":"月入2萬幾三十年都可以唔儲錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T18:08:35.000Z","msg":"賭撚哂啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T19:39:07.000Z","msg":"抵撚死"},{"pid":"9f183b90328d829f59e050a31b5790bce6cf2fe1","tid":1987833,"uid":30067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c829c3699f01cbd8124af196a4c79aea7fec3c98","tid":1987833,"uid":11285,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T17:57:17.000Z","msg":"月入2萬幾三十年都可以唔儲錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj